{"id":847814803,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"6 months, 1 week","timestamp":1669090481,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"59 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/847814803/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"10.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        unordered_map<char,bool> hset;\n        int start = -1;\n        int end = -1;\n        int ans = INT_MIN;\n        int count = 0;\n        for (int i = 0 ; i < s.length() ; i ++) {\n            char c = s[i];\n            if (hset.find(c) == hset.end()) {\n                end = i;\n                hset[c] = true;\n                count++;\n                if (start == -1)\n                    start = i;\n            }\n            else {\n                ans = max(ans,count);\n                count--;\n                char curr = s[start];\n                hset.erase(curr);\n                start++;\n                i--;\n            }\n        }\n\n        ans = max(ans,count);\n        \n        return ans;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false}
